cdata.name: Kepler
cdata.desc: Kepler is a platform that connects Robotics and AI startups to investors while allowing full transparency and traceability of investments. The services provided by Kepler include an internal exchange, a built-in wallet, an investment explorer, and templates of smart contracts to run fundraising campaigns and other tools to connect startups with all the actors involved in the investment sector. KEP token is the ERC20 token used as method to invest and to access the ecosystem of services provided by the Kepler platform.
